<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_81" id="40r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_81_r2l2">Elſpet <expan>B<ex>ur</ex>grefin</expan> / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_81_r2l3">Gnedige fraw / Als vns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnad aber <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat / von des </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l4"><expan>Cʒolln<ex>er</ex>s</expan> wegen cʒü vache / . Davon <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan> hochwirdıkeit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l6">vormals wol <expan>verſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vvie das beredt ıſt / . vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough"> als </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_81_r2l5">auch wie </ab></add> wir das </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l7">durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen beſtellet <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd getrawen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> gnaden vvol daʒ </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l10">Jr 
<del rend="strikethrough">laſſet </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_81_line_1576532306638_577">das </ab></add> alſo beſteen / vnd dabey <expan>beleıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add><ab facs="#facs_81_line_1576532311064_582">laſſen </ab></add> vnd vns des nicht für v̈bel </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_81_r2l11"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet / wan vvo etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> vj̃ <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan> <expan>Jnuocau<ex>i</ex><hi rend="sup">t</hi></expan> / </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_81" id="40r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Elspet <expan>b<ex>ur</ex>grefin</expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Gnedige fraw, als uns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnad aber
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> hat von des
                                <expan>czolln<ex>er</ex>s</expan> wegen czü Vache. Davon
                                <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        hochwirdikeit vormals wol <expan>verschrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, wie das
                        beredt ist und <add>auch wie</add> wir das durch
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> willen bestellet
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>; und getrawen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
                        gnaden wol, daz ir <add>das</add> also besteen und dabey
                                <expan>beleib<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<add>lassen</add> und uns des nicht für übel <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        wöllet; wan wo etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>omi</ex>nica<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>invocav<ex>i</ex><hi rend="sup">t</hi></expan>.</ab>
</div>
